{
  "texts": [
    "Future research should also investigate longitudinal impacts, examining whether sustained TDD-LLM integration fosters enduring improvements in programming habits and critical thinking.",
    "Additionally, expanding the scope of inquiry to include comparative analyses across different LLM architectures and prompting strategies will deepen our understanding of optimal practices.",
    "Ultimately, this work seeks to contribute broadly to the ongoing dialogue on integrating AI responsibly within technical education and professional development.",
    "We look forward to engaging with a diverse community to refine and evolve this framework collaboratively.",
